169
00:07:49.603 --> 00:07:54.508
Well. so. as a business major
with a minor in graphic design.

170
00:07:54.642 --> 00:07:57.311
I'm always looking for gaps
in supply side markets

171
00:07:57.445 --> 00:08:02.416
to use my specific skill
set to fulfill the unique needs
of college students.

172
00:08:02.550 --> 00:08:03.884
You make fake IDs.

173
00:08:04.018 --> 00:08:06.153
That is a federal crime.
Badger.

174
00:08:06.988 --> 00:08:08.856
